I bought the kit at a large discount. I wasn't sure how well it would work because I've never used teeth Whitening products. This product is easy to use and doesn't take a lot of time. 
I have somewhat sensitive teeth and this has given me no problems at all. Also, my teeth were never very white so I wasn't expecting a movie star smile. 
The results have been surprisingly very good, although not bright white, my teeth are noticeably whiter and I am very pleased.

2.  Table will not hold a lot of weight. But honeycomb structure under the tabletop means a structurally flat surface.

4. However, the table has no latching or locking mechanism when open. Which means if you try and move the table two people have to hold it using the far ends or the table will start to fold up. This will dump whatever is on the table to the ground and may damage whatever falls.

5. Otherwise very light weight for carrying and great as a display table at craft fairs or business booths.

column25: worth the money for general traveling
column26: So, I bought the set for the color %26 pattern because I knew I wanted to paint on them. Great find for under $100. Used the smallest for a carry-on for a long weekend and was able to stuff it without any issues to the case or zipper. The largest took its turn for a week long trip and came home just fine. Really great movement without having to drag it behind you. The lock is a bonus for air travel, tho I usually secure again with zip ties. Wouldn't let a gorilla play with this luggage but it is a good set for general traveling and nestles well for storage.
